Intro4
------------------------------------------------------------------------
"Captain, the damage to the ship is irreversible. Cosmodog is gone. Leaving the planet will not be possible."


You clench your teeth and try to calm down. "Not with this attitude, Luke." 


Suddenly, an alert message appears on the console in front of you, coloring the inside of the cabin in a demonic red tinge. Your heart skips a beat. "They have a lock on!" you whisper. Apparently, the destruction of the ship was not enough for the guardian. You close your eyes and brace for impact... 


But it never comes.


Not after a second. Not after ten. You anxiously listen to the silence, wondering what is going on.


"Intercepting a command transmission to the guardian satellite." Luke's voice is still annoyingly calm and emotionless. "Something is taking control over the satellite's weapon systems. There is a comment message. It says: An emergency pod. Possible survivors. God protects the wary." 


...